The '''Valley of Umbra''' was a valley of [[Zelos II]], home to [[Zelosian]]s, where an "abandoned" [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Mining/Legends|mining]] and military base was hidden. This was the place where the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] fought the Galactic Empire.

